Subject: [PATCH] feat: import blood pressure from Health Connect into the Lab
 Book

Maps each BloodPressureRecord to the Lab Book's systolic+diastolic row pair
(same shape the manual marker editor writes) with deterministic ids so
re-imports upsert instead of duplicating. Unit-tested without a client via
HealthConnectImporter.bloodPressureRows().
